text:

3. Suspended Grant runner files temporary restraining order , attempting to run in Wednesday's PIL cross country championship meet
4. Portland Thorns will trade Alex Morgan to Orlando Pride
5. Ducks players believe they can run the table to Pac-12 title game: Oregon rundown
